{"tid":2380543,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"抗爭印記@Google Street View","createTime":"2021-01-26T03:27:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T04:44:13.000Z","uid":193456,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b177727c474f767426b8b0ab9fe5a95df7c4a30f","tid":2380543,"uid":193456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T03:27:44.000Z","msg":"原來Google Street View靜靜雞更新左好多2019年影落既街景<br />\n當中唔少係10月打得最金最激時既印記<br />\n小弟一丁友未必發掘得晒咁多<br />\n加上隨時被藍屍黑狗舉報<br />\n希望有心巴打幫手搵搵cap低<br />\n雖然今日5毛PR四圍鬥黃至撚黑暗好絕望<br />\n但唔好忘記當日手足兄弟爬山不分化<br />\n香港人點都會再企起身幫共產黨釘佢老母蓋<br />\n<strong>黎明點都會黎到光復香港</strong><br />\n龍翔道光時<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o0MACLt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo0MACLt.jpg&h=54b5c1c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/thYGyqP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FthYGyqP.jpg&h=148e6746&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8aJvrXp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8aJvrXp.jpg&h=45f10dfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 淘大連儂牆<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EWgQrEL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEWgQrEL.jpg&h=192c5f41&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n太子831祭壇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qg9VCNf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqg9VCNf.jpg&h=3d8cec15&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n太子831祭壇ver2<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DZy3MF6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDZy3MF6.jpg&h=b37ba77a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nMK街訪橋底<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SgvqfAo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSgvqfAo.jpg&h=9554fedb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xaKKv9O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxaKKv9O.jpg&h=620dc432&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n狗鐵裝修<br